column5: We are going to Abamasagi Lake.  Flying out of Nakina July 12th until July 19th. Leaving the Niagara area at 12am Friday.  Call Doug 716-417-3841 or pm me if interested.
Sorry, might be dumb questions:  What are you fishing for How much $ How many other people are going What is included, what do you need to bring?  More information would help!

hi cliff walleye and pike 700 per person right now we have 5 we take my suburban 4 of us spilt gas. 4 ways half a motel in nakina.boat, gas, cabin is included you bring your fishing gear and food.i did a post 2 ago about this lake thanks doug
Cliff, Doug is a great guy to spend time with, in my opinion.
I am sure he is, unfortunatly I can't make it but hopfully someone on here can take advantage of the opportunity!
Someone had better jump on this. I'm working then so I can't go. Grab it. the place is perfect, the price is great and you can trust Doug. Dang I wish I could go.....
I can vouch for the lake, it's a gem! $700 is a sweet deal for a fly-in anywhere
Can vouch for both the lake (incredible!) and Doug.  If I had the time I'd be all over this.
spot is filled thank's for the reply's and OFC
